@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<style>
    main {
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #0000A0; /* Dark-blue background color */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        color: white;
    }

    section {
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: #428BCA; /* Light-blue background color for the section */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
    }

        h3::after {
            content: "\25BC";
            font-size: 20px;
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

    .dropdown-content {
        display: none;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .show {
        display: block;
    }
</style>

<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title VMed Medical Imaging Group</h2>

    <p>
        At VMed Medical Imaging Group, we are dedicated to advancing healthcare through state-of-the-art MRI (Magnetic Resonance
        Imaging) technology. Our commitment to providing exceptional medical imaging services has made us a trusted partner for
        patients and healthcare professionals alike.
    </p>

    <section>
        <h3 onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">Our Mission</h3>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
            <!-- Add the "show" class to make it the default -->
            <p>
                Our mission is simple yet profound: to offer accurate, detailed, and compassionate MRI imaging services that empower
                patients and healthcare providers with the information they need to make informed decisions about their health.
                We believe in the power of medical imaging to transform healthcare, and we are passionate about delivering the highest
                quality care to every individual we serve.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3 onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">Cutting-Edge MRI Technology</h3>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
            <p>
                We understand that medical imaging plays a pivotal role in diagnosis and treatment planning. That's why we invest in
                the latest MRI technology, ensuring that our patients receive the most precise and comprehensive imaging available.
                Our state-of-the-art MRI scanners are designed to capture detailed images of the body's internal structures, helping
                healthcare professionals detect and evaluate a wide range of medical conditions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3 onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">Expertise and Compassion</h3>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
            <p>
                At VMed, we are more than just a medical imaging facility – we are a team of dedicated professionals who care deeply
                about our patients. Our experienced radiologists and technologists are committed to providing a comfortable and
                reassuring experience during your MRI procedure. We understand that undergoing medical imaging can be an anxious
                time, and we are here to answer your questions and address your concerns with empathy and expertise.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3 onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">Patient-Centered Care</h3>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
            <p>
                We place our patients at the center of everything we do. From the moment you schedule your MRI appointment to the
                delivery of your results, our focus is on your well-being. Our friendly and knowledgeable staff will guide you
                through the process, ensuring that you feel informed and supported every step of the way.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3 onclick="toggleDropdown(this)">Collaborative Healthcare</h3>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
            <p>
                VMed Medical Imaging Group collaborates closely with referring physicians and healthcare providers to ensure that
                the MRI imaging we provide is integrated seamlessly into your overall healthcare plan. We believe in the importance
                of a collaborative approach to healthcare, and we provide timely, accurate reports to your healthcare team to
                facilitate diagnosis and treatment.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<script>
    function toggleDropdown(element) {
        var content = element.nextElementSibling;
        if (content.style.display === "block") {
            content.style.display = "none";
            element.querySelector('::after').style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        } else {
            content.style.display = "block";
            element.querySelector('::after').style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
        }
    }
</script>
